{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"af5ae44efe","title":"八·二七指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4ba0a4c5e5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":27,"articleId":"af5ae44efe"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7dc26de34","type":"title","text":"八·二七指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"ed8533e1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"一、许世友要帮助过关，他是一个战将，文化革命以来，落后了，跟不上；","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"a2921c1b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要出马恩列斯语录；","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"18f5165e6f","type":"paragraph","text":"三、文化大革命要搞三年，一年发动，一年胜利，一年扫尾","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"c32305eff2","type":"paragraph","text":"四、天津南开大学卫东红卫兵写了一篇好文章（指《要大胆使用革命干部》），提出了一个新问题，红卫兵小报是好东西；","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"9d48640359","type":"paragraph","text":"五、不要把党内一小摄走资派和军内一小摄走资派并提，只提党内一小摄，把解放军搞跨了还要不要政府；","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"11ec7ff9b4","type":"paragraph","text":"六、群众组织提以我为核心，这样提是极的","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"7b8a1ac0b3","type":"paragraph","text":"七、依靠青年人","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"58b1d22310","type":"paragraph","text":"八、依靠群众，加强专政，新疆办大型劳改农场不一定好，要研究；","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"},{"id":"72e4d5dfcb","type":"paragraph","text":"九、要抓学习，把工作做好，要精兵简政","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe"}],"page":{"id":"816b9f6a32","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"af5ae44efe","start":59,"end":59}}}},"__N_SSG":true}